snippet.title: Resident Evil Re:Verse - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available for free to owners of Resident Evil Village, Resident Evil RE:Verse is a survival revenge battle game in which two-to-six players fight to the death.
Familiar characters and terrifying creatures from the Resident Evil series clash in high-stakes battles where death is not the end.

https://www.residentevil.com/reverse/us/

#Capcom #ResidentEvil #ResidentEvilREVerse
